   [;m│[0m  Views                                                                                                         [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m                                                                                                                [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m  Hive has two main layouts:                                                                                    [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m                                                                                                                [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m    tab    Sidebar view — tree of projects and sessions with a live preview pane.                               [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m    g     Grid view    — compact cells showing all sessions in the current project.                             [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m    G     All-sessions grid — every session across all projects.                                                [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m                                                                                                                [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m  Navigation                                                                                                    [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m                                                                                                                [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m    ↑ / k        move up                                                                                        [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m    ↓ / j        move down                                                                                      [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m    [ / ]        jump to previous / next project                                                                [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m    space         toggle project collapse                                                                       [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m    ←  / →        collapse / expand project                                                                     [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m    tab          switch between sidebar and preview pane                                                        [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m                                                                                                                [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m  Projects & Sessions                                                                                           [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m                                                                                                                [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m    p    new project (choose directory)                                                                         [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m    n    new session in the current project                                                                     [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m    W    new worktree session (new git branch + directory)                                                      [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m    r    rename project or session                                                                              [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m    x    kill session                                                                                           [;m│[0m   
   [;m│[0m                                                                                                                [;m│[0m   
